fields.name: IPAddress
fields.description: An IP Address that Domain Name currently resolves to.

fields.name: IsAccessible
fields.description: Whether it is possible to create a TCP connection from the App Service Environment to this IpAddress at this Port.

fields.name: Latency
fields.description: The time in milliseconds it takes for a TCP connection to be created from the App Service Environment to this IpAddress at this Port.

fields.name: Port
fields.description: The port an endpoint is connected to.
